[Juwu Real Estate Agency]

163
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:41,510
My husband is going to be a solo hero.

164
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,940
I have to support him.

165
00:08:41,770 --> 00:08:45,160
[Stage Two of Kangcheng International]

166
