224
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:18,040
You...

225
00:11:18,330 --> 00:11:19,870
You can say I have no guts.

226
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:24,490
[Crafts and Hearts]

227
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:22,030
